WEBVTT

00:00:19.185 --> 00:00:20.186
Gu-cheon.

00:00:21.646 --> 00:00:22.897
Are you all right?

00:00:23.398 --> 00:00:26.192
There was a reason the Crown Prince's spirit

00:00:26.276 --> 00:00:27.944
Summoned the pestilent-gwis.

00:00:29.863 --> 00:00:32.657
A great calamity will soon fall upon the entire palace.

00:01:20.872 --> 00:01:24.417
Your Majesty, that seat is

00:01:44.813 --> 00:01:50.485
His Majesty's life is in peril.

00:01:50.568 --> 00:01:52.112
Your Majesty.

00:01:52.195 --> 00:01:56.449
- That is not-- - I already know everything.

00:01:58.952 --> 00:02:02.372
That the spirit seeks to kill the King.

00:02:03.957 --> 00:02:08.837
There is no one but me who can take this vacant throne.

00:02:09.629 --> 00:02:11.673
No one but me.

00:02:12.966 --> 00:02:14.759
Only I

00:02:15.260 --> 00:02:20.682
Can protect this palace and the royal house!

00:02:21.182 --> 00:02:22.892
Only me!

00:02:23.810 --> 00:02:25.436
I alone

00:02:26.646 --> 00:02:31.151
I alone can protect them. I alone.

00:02:32.026 --> 00:02:33.111
No one but me

00:02:35.572 --> 00:02:36.781
- Councillor! - Councillor!

00:02:36.865 --> 00:02:38.825
- Councillor! - Left State Councillor!

00:02:39.534 --> 00:02:41.494
- Councillor! - Councillor.

00:02:44.497 --> 00:02:46.291
Councillor, are you all right?

00:03:33.213 --> 00:03:39.135
THE EAST PALACE

00:03:39.219 --> 00:03:43.014
Could the Crown Prince be connected to what is happening in the palace?

00:03:44.641 --> 00:03:45.642
Gu-cheon?

00:03:47.143 --> 00:03:48.102
Gu-cheon.

00:03:51.481 --> 00:03:53.233
What did you just say?

00:03:54.651 --> 00:03:58.321
Something is not right in the palace, but you do not look well either.

00:04:01.950 --> 00:04:04.452
It is because the Crown Prince's spirit has grown stronger.

00:04:06.955 --> 00:04:10.083
That is why I will seal him here.

00:04:10.166 --> 00:04:12.835
Seal him? Instead of sending his soul to the afterlife?

00:04:12.919 --> 00:04:14.837
Impossible. He devoured the pestilent-gwis.

00:04:14.921 --> 00:04:17.465
Their souls are now tangled with his.

00:04:19.592 --> 00:04:21.010
Good grief.

00:04:21.594 --> 00:04:24.013
Do not look at me as though I am about to die.

00:04:27.433 --> 00:04:29.394
And stop frowning. You look ugly.

00:04:29.477 --> 00:04:32.397
You have not looked well since you acquired the gwi-mae's eyes.

00:04:34.190 --> 00:04:35.650
Like the gwi-mae from the well

00:04:35.733 --> 00:04:39.404
Are you afraid I might lose my mind and kill someone?

00:04:43.366 --> 00:04:44.701
That will not happen.

00:04:45.743 --> 00:04:49.998
Sealing a spirit is a hundred times easier than destroying it.

00:04:50.081 --> 00:04:52.208
Sealing him away will do.

00:04:54.168 --> 00:04:55.586
It will work, will it not?

00:04:56.170 --> 00:04:58.423
The appeasement rite will be of great help.

00:05:01.009 --> 00:05:03.303
If we soothe the souls of the pestilent-gwis,

00:05:03.803 --> 00:05:05.930
We can weaken the Crown Prince's spirit.

00:05:08.349 --> 00:05:10.435
I will walk you back to your quarters.

00:05:10.518 --> 00:05:12.437
No need. It is not like I am ill.

00:05:17.233 --> 00:05:18.776
But you are.

00:05:23.948 --> 00:05:27.535
It will all be over by tonight.

00:05:28.119 --> 00:05:31.080
That is right. Sink or swim.

00:05:33.666 --> 00:05:36.753
What will you do after this is over and you leave the palace?

00:05:38.254 --> 00:05:42.216
I will drink myself senseless and sleep for days.

00:05:42.967 --> 00:05:44.427
That is not what I mean.

00:05:45.470 --> 00:05:47.013
How do you wish to live?

00:05:47.638 --> 00:05:49.515
And what do you wish to do with your life?

00:05:52.018 --> 00:05:53.686
I have never thought about it.

00:05:54.562 --> 00:05:56.314
But I will return to the temple.

00:05:57.190 --> 00:06:00.360
What? You said you hated the head monk,

00:06:00.443 --> 00:06:02.111
And yet you are going back?

00:06:02.862 --> 00:06:03.863
You see,

00:06:04.572 --> 00:06:07.116
About four <i>Ri </i>southeast of the temple,

00:06:07.617 --> 00:06:10.453
There is a river running along a sheer cliff.

00:06:11.537 --> 00:06:12.830
And that is

00:06:15.041 --> 00:06:17.126
Where my mother died.

00:06:20.296 --> 00:06:23.007
So even in death, I cannot leave the temple.

00:06:27.804 --> 00:06:29.055
I am sorry.

00:06:34.602 --> 00:06:36.896
I dragged you into the matter of the palace spirit.

00:06:38.356 --> 00:06:41.567
- You have nothing to do-- - You have already used me all you wanted.

00:06:41.651 --> 00:06:42.860
It is a bit late for that.

00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:48.574
You still choose only harsh words, even at the very end.

00:06:49.158 --> 00:06:51.452
I finally found the courage to be honest with you.

00:06:53.371 --> 00:06:57.917
Tonight, you will die.

00:06:59.085 --> 00:07:01.796
The one who failed to die with his mother.

00:07:02.839 --> 00:07:05.591
The one who was never meant to live,

00:07:06.175 --> 00:07:10.430
Neither human nor spirit.

00:07:12.515 --> 00:07:16.185
Tonight, you will die.

00:07:16.769 --> 00:07:19.730
The one who failed to die with his mother.

00:07:19.814 --> 00:07:22.108
The one who was never meant to live,

00:07:23.901 --> 00:07:29.824
Neither human nor spirit.

00:07:30.700 --> 00:07:33.411
You will die.

00:07:35.163 --> 00:07:37.874
What did Gosuyeochil say, Princess?

00:07:41.878 --> 00:07:48.468
<i>Turtle, Turtle</i>

00:07:48.968 --> 00:07:54.557
<i>Poke your head out</i>

00:07:55.141 --> 00:08:00.313
<i>If you do not</i>

00:08:00.813 --> 00:08:06.360
<i>I will roast you and eat you up</i>

00:08:06.861 --> 00:08:08.279
Is it nearly ready?

00:08:09.030 --> 00:08:11.491
The ritual will begin soon, at the Hour of the Ox.

00:08:12.116 --> 00:08:13.451
It is almost done.

00:08:33.471 --> 00:08:35.181
I have given it some thought.

00:08:37.683 --> 00:08:40.186
I will go with you to the Realm of Gwi.

00:08:44.899 --> 00:08:47.109
I have told you time and again

00:08:47.735 --> 00:08:49.904
That you will not last there.

00:08:50.863 --> 00:08:52.573
Do not even consider it.

00:09:02.500 --> 00:09:03.709
It is all set.

00:09:05.461 --> 00:09:06.587
I am heading out.

00:09:07.088 --> 00:09:08.506
Wait a moment.

00:09:15.137 --> 00:09:16.264
Drink this.

00:09:17.139 --> 00:09:19.100
This medicine will replenish your yang energy.

00:09:19.183 --> 00:09:20.643
It is made with rare ingredients.

00:09:22.687 --> 00:09:25.398
Well, you should not have

00:09:29.735 --> 00:09:32.530
You should have given it to me sooner.

00:09:35.283 --> 00:09:36.701
It is so bitter.

00:09:39.579 --> 00:09:41.664
Is there anything I can help you with?

00:09:45.585 --> 00:09:46.711
No.

00:09:48.588 --> 00:09:49.589
Princess.

00:09:50.089 --> 00:09:52.758
The Crown Prince's spirit is after you as well,

00:09:54.677 --> 00:09:56.387
So keep yourself well hidden.

00:10:06.814 --> 00:10:07.815
What is the matter?

00:10:10.735 --> 00:10:12.194
Before coming here,

00:10:13.446 --> 00:10:15.781
I visited my grandmother's quarters.

00:10:15.865 --> 00:10:17.199
Why did you go there?

00:10:17.992 --> 00:10:19.869
You treat her like an enemy

00:10:38.721 --> 00:10:41.140
You will not wake for half a day.

00:10:48.522 --> 00:10:49.357
Why?

00:10:50.941 --> 00:10:53.527
- Why - I do not know myself.

00:10:54.028 --> 00:10:57.406
The moment I heard the gwi-mae say that you would die tonight,

00:10:57.490 --> 00:10:59.659
I moved before I could even think.

00:11:06.499 --> 00:11:09.377
You are the only one in this palace I can trust and rely on.

00:11:09.960 --> 00:11:11.003
So

00:11:13.673 --> 00:11:15.841
I will not stand by and let you die.

00:11:21.055 --> 00:11:23.015
I will save you

00:11:24.308 --> 00:11:26.143
Even if it means sacrificing my life.

00:11:41.701 --> 00:11:44.203
Thank you for protecting me all this time.

00:11:52.211 --> 00:11:54.130
From this moment forward,

00:11:55.506 --> 00:11:57.550
I will take over your duties.

00:12:23.701 --> 00:12:25.953
The appeasement rite will begin soon.

00:12:26.454 --> 00:12:29.290
It seems the shaman has a clever plan.

00:13:27.723 --> 00:13:28.724
Your Majesty.

00:13:29.475 --> 00:13:31.268
Do not make a scene.

00:13:49.829 --> 00:13:51.997
The Crown Prince is here.

00:15:00.482 --> 00:15:03.235
So, you have become an ak-gwi after all.

00:15:04.945 --> 00:15:06.572
Do not even think of interfering.

00:15:07.823 --> 00:15:09.575
You must feel wronged and resentful.

00:15:10.701 --> 00:15:12.202
I understand that as well.

00:15:13.621 --> 00:15:16.332
You were killed by your own father, so it is only natural.

00:15:21.003 --> 00:15:21.879
Brother!

00:15:26.342 --> 00:15:29.011
He abandoned me because I could hear the voices of the dead,

00:15:30.220 --> 00:15:32.431
And he let my mother die.

00:15:32.514 --> 00:15:35.267
I despise Father as well. Brother!

00:15:43.442 --> 00:15:45.527
I told you not to interfere.

00:19:03.225 --> 00:19:05.185
<i>I will not stand by and let you die.</i>

00:19:06.979 --> 00:19:08.981
<i>Even if it means sacrificing my life.</i>

00:19:43.140 --> 00:19:44.975
Are you telling me not to do it?

00:19:55.777 --> 00:19:58.572
This is the only way to save the Princess.

00:20:03.368 --> 00:20:05.329
She was willing to risk her life for me,

00:20:06.872 --> 00:20:08.290
So I must do the same.

00:21:10.185 --> 00:21:11.687
<i>Humans.</i>

00:21:12.729 --> 00:21:17.025
<i>They move toward death</i> <i>from the moment they are born.</i>

00:21:19.111 --> 00:21:21.029
<i>One's status</i>

00:21:21.905 --> 00:21:24.074
<i>or character</i>

00:21:25.033 --> 00:21:26.660
<i>does not matter.</i>

00:21:31.123 --> 00:21:35.043
<i>In the end, death comes equally to all,</i>

00:21:36.253 --> 00:21:37.879
<i>so there is no need to grieve</i>

00:21:38.588 --> 00:21:40.757
<i>or feel wronged.</i>

00:23:00.837 --> 00:23:03.548
No wonder the palace is thick with Yin energy.

00:23:04.841 --> 00:23:06.385
So it was you.

00:23:07.552 --> 00:23:09.054
Primordial Gwi-mae.

00:23:12.307 --> 00:23:13.642
I will give you

00:23:14.267 --> 00:23:16.144
Whatever you want.

00:23:16.645 --> 00:23:17.687
In return,

00:23:19.064 --> 00:23:20.857
Grant me your power

00:23:22.526 --> 00:23:24.277
So that I can save the Princess.

00:27:18.261 --> 00:27:21.848
How much longer, Your Majesty?

00:27:38.657 --> 00:27:41.159
<i>To stop the pestilence,</i>

00:27:42.327 --> 00:27:46.456
<i>I first placed you, the powerless,</i> <i>before the blade.</i>

00:27:47.582 --> 00:27:50.210
<i>Without asking your leave,</i>

00:27:51.127 --> 00:27:52.879
<i>I shattered your fates.</i>

00:27:55.757 --> 00:27:58.760
<i>And yet, I was unable to stop anything.</i>

00:27:59.552 --> 00:28:04.099
<i>All I hear are your resentful wails.</i>

00:28:09.396 --> 00:28:11.815
This is a sin that can never

00:28:15.485 --> 00:28:16.653
Be washed away.

00:28:19.322 --> 00:28:22.325
<i>I do not mean to seek forgiveness.</i>

00:28:24.035 --> 00:28:26.079
If you wish

00:28:29.999 --> 00:28:32.293
You may take my life at once.

00:28:36.464 --> 00:28:38.800
<i>Yet if my life is spared,</i>

00:28:40.260 --> 00:28:42.971
<i>I shall embrace those</i> <i>left behind by your deaths.</i>

00:28:44.222 --> 00:28:45.223
<i>Your parents,</i>

00:28:46.182 --> 00:28:47.225
<i>siblings,</i>

00:28:48.435 --> 00:28:49.436
<i>children,</i>

00:28:49.936 --> 00:28:51.938
And all your kin.

00:28:54.482 --> 00:28:56.568
I shall care for them until the very end

00:29:01.281 --> 00:29:04.784
As the parent of this nation.

00:29:13.168 --> 00:29:16.296
<i>And for this sin</i> <i>I could not pay for in this life,</i>

00:29:17.714 --> 00:29:20.759
I shall answer for it again and again in the afterlife.

00:29:24.095 --> 00:29:26.473
So let go of your lingering resentment

00:29:30.268 --> 00:29:32.020
And move on to the afterlife.

00:29:35.440 --> 00:29:37.734
<i>Now lay down that heavy burden</i>

00:29:39.611 --> 00:29:41.613
<i>here in this world</i>

00:29:44.783 --> 00:29:46.326
<i>and pass on</i>

00:29:50.038 --> 00:29:51.664
<i>to the other side.</i>

00:30:34.499 --> 00:30:38.920
I have been waiting for the pestilent-gwis to leave.

00:31:53.286 --> 00:31:54.495
It cannot

00:31:56.372 --> 00:31:58.625
It cannot end like this.

00:32:11.346 --> 00:32:13.473
Do you wish to kill your father that much?

00:32:15.433 --> 00:32:16.935
You see

00:32:19.437 --> 00:32:22.690
I have been tormented all my life, believing that I killed my mother.

00:32:24.025 --> 00:32:25.985
Fearing that sin would turn me into an ak-gwi,

00:32:26.069 --> 00:32:29.948
I have forced myself to live on so that I would not become like you.

00:32:31.324 --> 00:32:35.078
But why would you go so far as to become an ak-gwi

00:32:57.642 --> 00:32:59.852
I wanted to be King.

00:33:01.562 --> 00:33:04.273
But none of that matters now.

00:33:05.274 --> 00:33:08.528
This palace, where I cannot become King.

00:33:09.904 --> 00:33:11.906
Those lowly subjects.

00:33:15.284 --> 00:33:16.703
Those within the palace

00:33:20.289 --> 00:33:23.001
And those beyond its walls

00:33:25.211 --> 00:33:26.963
I will kill them all.

00:33:31.134 --> 00:33:34.595
Destroying your soul was the one thing I wished to avoid.

00:33:35.388 --> 00:33:37.765
You cannot destroy me.

00:33:38.474 --> 00:33:40.518
If you destroy someone's soul,

00:33:40.601 --> 00:33:44.230
You will, in turn, become an ak-gwi as well.

00:33:55.158 --> 00:33:56.659
I know.

00:33:57.577 --> 00:33:59.620
But if I do not kill you,

00:33:59.704 --> 00:34:01.873
The curse will not be broken, and the Princess will die.

00:34:03.499 --> 00:34:06.252
From the moment I met Primordial Gwi-mae,

00:34:06.753 --> 00:34:08.838
I was prepared to become an ak-gwi!

00:35:04.060 --> 00:35:05.895
It is all over.

00:35:27.083 --> 00:35:29.210
Councillor!

00:35:46.978 --> 00:35:48.020
Chief Eunuch Kim!

00:35:51.607 --> 00:35:52.650
Your Majesty.

00:36:05.788 --> 00:36:07.498
Gu-cheon!

00:37:18.819 --> 00:37:21.656
I will give you all the yang energy I have left

00:37:28.412 --> 00:37:29.872
So go back.

00:38:26.762 --> 00:38:28.306
Gu-cheon, please wake up.

00:38:28.889 --> 00:38:29.890
Gu-cheon.

00:38:44.280 --> 00:38:47.158
Take my yang energy.

00:38:50.661 --> 00:38:52.872
You cannot die like this.

00:38:53.497 --> 00:38:55.124
I will not let you go.

00:38:56.292 --> 00:38:57.293
No.

00:38:59.420 --> 00:39:00.338
No.

00:39:02.590 --> 00:39:03.632
Gu-cheon.

00:39:10.723 --> 00:39:12.516
That is enough.

00:39:30.409 --> 00:39:32.244
Now that it has come to this,

00:39:32.912 --> 00:39:35.081
Let us go all out.

00:39:35.581 --> 00:39:37.208
I have already become an ak-gwi.

00:39:37.291 --> 00:39:39.668
Rather than let a gwi-mae devour my soul

00:40:01.273 --> 00:40:02.149
Your Majesty.

00:40:02.650 --> 00:40:05.986
There have been no further reports of the pestilence.

00:40:06.487 --> 00:40:08.906
The rites in each region concluded without issue,

00:40:08.989 --> 00:40:12.618
And the unrest among the people is settling.

00:40:13.119 --> 00:40:14.870
Very well.

00:40:15.663 --> 00:40:17.289
You may leave.

00:40:24.755 --> 00:40:25.840
Your Majesty.

00:40:27.466 --> 00:40:30.344
All the strange calamities in the palace over the past few days

00:40:31.220 --> 00:40:33.013
Have ceased.

00:40:46.610 --> 00:40:47.736
Let us go.

00:41:00.082 --> 00:41:01.000
<i>However,</i>

00:41:02.960 --> 00:41:05.212
<i>the Queen Dowager,</i> <i>now at her private residence,</i>

00:41:06.297 --> 00:41:08.507
<i>is not of sound mind.</i>

00:41:16.432 --> 00:41:18.726
<i>How is Prince Iksang?</i>

00:41:23.772 --> 00:41:25.441
<i>He is under secret investigation</i>

00:41:26.525 --> 00:41:31.363
<i>for summoning a shaman</i> <i>to perform rites against Your Majesty.</i>

00:41:34.366 --> 00:41:35.659
Very well.

00:41:36.577 --> 00:41:37.953
You may leave.

00:41:39.622 --> 00:41:41.290
It has been three days.

00:41:50.841 --> 00:41:52.051
Princess.

00:41:55.137 --> 00:41:58.307
Perhaps it is time to give up on him.

00:42:03.103 --> 00:42:05.272
We thought he was dead last time,

00:42:06.357 --> 00:42:07.900
And yet he woke up, did he not?

00:42:08.400 --> 00:42:10.694
Even for Gu-cheon

00:42:13.989 --> 00:42:15.115
Everyone is saying

00:42:16.033 --> 00:42:18.661
That he is dead.

00:42:21.121 --> 00:42:22.665
Do not cry.

00:42:25.084 --> 00:42:26.001
He is not dead.

00:42:40.307 --> 00:42:41.392
Look.

00:42:43.894 --> 00:42:45.104
The child is crying.

00:42:46.939 --> 00:42:50.609
So please stop troubling us any further and return now.

00:42:57.032 --> 00:42:59.201
If you cannot find your way back

00:43:01.495 --> 00:43:05.124
Then ring the bell so that I may find you.

00:43:24.518 --> 00:43:25.936
Ggeomeoksali.

00:43:26.562 --> 00:43:30.190
That one is called Ggeomeoksali. It is no ordinary creature.

00:43:30.274 --> 00:43:33.485
It attaches to the living, not places, feeding on yang energy.

00:43:34.194 --> 00:43:35.487
The living

00:43:39.408 --> 00:43:40.951
He is alive.

00:43:55.549 --> 00:43:58.052
<i>About four </i>ri <i>southeast of the temple,</i>

00:43:58.552 --> 00:44:01.138
<i>there is a river</i> <i>running along a sheer cliff.</i>

00:44:04.224 --> 00:44:05.434
<i>And that is</i>

00:44:06.185 --> 00:44:08.520
<i>where my mother died.</i>

00:44:09.772 --> 00:44:12.650
<i>So even in death,</i> <i>I cannot leave the temple.</i>

00:44:27.790 --> 00:44:28.791
Please

00:44:53.190 --> 00:44:54.775
I knew you would be here.

00:45:04.576 --> 00:45:06.120
It is all over.

00:45:09.415 --> 00:45:11.583
You can now leave the palace

00:45:13.377 --> 00:45:15.003
As you wished.

00:45:15.838 --> 00:45:16.922
So

00:45:18.507 --> 00:45:20.217
Do not stay here alone

00:45:22.136 --> 00:45:23.804
And come back with me.

00:45:26.223 --> 00:45:29.393
You said you were living without purpose, just existing.

00:45:29.893 --> 00:45:30.853
But live on.

00:45:33.188 --> 00:45:35.482
You may still live like a spirit.

00:45:37.317 --> 00:45:38.235
But live on!

00:45:41.989 --> 00:45:43.991
Are you listening to me?

00:46:15.397 --> 00:46:18.650
You said that your own life mattered more than anything, did you not?

00:46:20.986 --> 00:46:23.447
Did you think I would be glad

00:46:26.158 --> 00:46:28.202
If you threw your life away to save me?

00:46:47.221 --> 00:46:48.472
You wretch.

00:46:50.307 --> 00:46:53.727
Come back at once before I drag you out myself!

00:47:46.154 --> 00:47:47.322
Princess.

00:48:26.278 --> 00:48:27.279
Good grief.

00:48:33.201 --> 00:48:34.620
So noisy.

00:48:40.250 --> 00:48:41.543
You are crying again.

00:49:30.884 --> 00:49:32.719
You made it back.

00:49:35.472 --> 00:49:37.557
Have you made all your preparations to leave?

00:49:38.225 --> 00:49:39.518
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:49:42.312 --> 00:49:43.438
However,

00:49:45.148 --> 00:49:47.192
This is quite a grand send-off.

00:49:51.279 --> 00:49:55.200
So you do not intend to let me go so easily, do you?

00:49:55.701 --> 00:49:58.578
I know what you went through

00:50:00.789 --> 00:50:03.250
In secret here.

00:50:03.333 --> 00:50:04.668
And you know

00:50:06.253 --> 00:50:08.797
Far too much about the palace and about me

00:50:11.967 --> 00:50:14.386
Do you not?

00:50:20.600 --> 00:50:21.560
Rise.

00:50:26.815 --> 00:50:28.942
People change

00:50:30.527 --> 00:50:32.112
Once they get what they want.

00:50:33.530 --> 00:50:36.491
Your promise meant little, Your Majesty.

00:50:51.048 --> 00:50:52.924
Are you seeing something again?

00:50:55.677 --> 00:50:56.845
The spirits of past Kings

00:50:58.305 --> 00:51:02.684
And the countless Princes who never became King linger here.

00:51:20.827 --> 00:51:22.287
You may leave now.

00:51:22.370 --> 00:51:24.456
Are you sparing me?

00:51:31.963 --> 00:51:33.673
We shall see.

00:51:56.738 --> 00:52:00.450
He would not suddenly change his mind and kill me, would he?

00:52:04.663 --> 00:52:05.789
Good grief.

00:52:13.922 --> 00:52:15.423
Why are you still standing there?

00:52:20.846 --> 00:52:22.806
Have you grown attached to the palace?

00:52:25.392 --> 00:52:26.518
Are you going somewhere?

00:52:27.769 --> 00:52:29.271
I am coming with you.

00:52:29.354 --> 00:52:30.313
What?

00:52:31.398 --> 00:52:32.274
Why?

00:52:41.241 --> 00:52:44.327
You went out of your way to help me settle my affairs.

00:52:45.745 --> 00:52:47.664
Now it is my turn to help you.

00:52:49.332 --> 00:52:50.250
Goodness.

00:52:56.631 --> 00:52:58.091
It will not be easy.

00:52:59.593 --> 00:53:01.970
Do not whine to me later about how hard it is.

00:53:07.601 --> 00:53:08.643
Let us go.

00:53:12.189 --> 00:53:13.023
Goodness.

00:53:50.310 --> 00:53:55.232
THE EAST PALACE

00:56:52.117 --> 00:56:55.370
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang

